Invocation Name: feed me
Developer Terms of Use
des:
Your favorite Food delivery app just got smarter. FoodChoo on demand now is pretty handy when it comes to ordering food. Thanks to a handful of Alexa skills produced by our team, you can order your favorite meals and drinks by speaking to the Amazon voice assistant.

With the FoodChoo on demand now skill, you can build a new order from scratch, and satiate your hunger. To get started, just say “Alexa, Feed me.” Alexa will connect you to our riders that are in your radius and get you ordering and tracking in no time. Once you have opened the app, you just have to say: "I’m hungry" and Alexa will ask you your preference. Reply with what you’d like to eat and Alexa will present to you with the menu options in your area.
